{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be3e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2199"},"text":"§ 2199.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Disclosure","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be3f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In accordance with regulations of the Farm Credit Administration, qualified lenders shall provide to borrowers, for all loans that are not subject to the Truth in Lending Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1601"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 1601","children":[],"tail":" et seq.), meaningful and timely disclosure not later than the time of the loan closing, of—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be40-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the current rate of interest on the loan;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be41-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of an adjustable or variable rate loan, the amount and frequency by which the interest rate can be increased during the term of the loan or, if there are no such limitations, a statement to that effect, and the factors (including the cost of funds, operating expenses, and provision for loan losses) that will be taken into account by the qualified lender in determining adjustments to the interest rate;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be42-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the effect, as shown by a representative example or examples, of any loan origination charges or purchases of stock or participation certificates on the effective rate of interest;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be43-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any change in the interest rate applicable to the borrower’s loan, and notice to the borrower of a change in the interest rate applicable to the loan of the borrower may be made within a reasonable time after the effective date of an increase or decrease in the interest rate;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be44-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" except with respect to stock guaranteed under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2162"},"text":"section 2162 of this title","children":[],"tail":", a statement indicating that stock that is purchased is at risk; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be45-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/a/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a statement indicating the various types of loan options available to borrowers, with an explanation of the terms and borrowers’ rights that apply to each type of loan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be46-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Differential interest rates","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"A qualified lender offering more than one rate of interest to borrowers shall, at the request of a borrower of a loan—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be47-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provide a review of the loan to determine if the proper interest rate has been established;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be48-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" explain to the borrower in writing the basis for the interest rate charged; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be49-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2199/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" explain to the borrower in writing how the credit status of the borrower may be improved to receive a lower interest rate on the loan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddcc8be4a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/181/tIV/s4"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–181, title IV, § 4","children":[],"tail":".13, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/205/tIII/s301/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–205, title III, § 301(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/1707"},"text":"99 Stat. 1707","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, title I","children":[],"tail":", §§ 103, 109, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/1579"},"text":"101 Stat. 1579","children":[],"tail":", 1584; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/105/tII/s207"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–105, title II, § 207","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/173"},"text":"110 Stat. 173","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddcc8be4b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddcc8be4c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddcc8be4d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Truth in Lending Act, referred to in subsec. (a), is title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/321"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–321","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-05-29"},"text":"May 29, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/146"},"text":"82 Stat. 146","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter I (§ 1601 et seq.) of chapter 41 of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1601"},"text":"section 1601 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"iddcc8be4e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 4.13 of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/181/tIV"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–181, title IV","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 1971","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/85/613"},"text":"85 Stat. 613","children":[],"tail":", was renumbered section 4.13B by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/205/tIII/s301/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–205, title III, § 301(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/1707"},"text":"99 Stat. 1707","children":[],"tail":", and is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2201"},"text":"section 2201 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddcc8be4f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (a)(4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/105"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–105","children":[],"tail":" inserted before semicolon at end “, and notice to the borrower of a change in the interest rate applicable to the loan of the borrower may be made within a reasonable time after the effective date of an increase or decrease in the interest rate”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/s109"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, § 109","children":[],"tail":", designated existing provisions as subsec. (a), inserted heading, and added subsec. (b)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/s103"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, § 103","children":[],"tail":", amended section generally, substituting introductory provisions and cls. (1) to (6) for former subsecs. (a) and (b)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddcc8be50-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"iddcc8be51-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective thirty days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1985","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/205/s401"},"text":"section 401 of Pub. L. 99–205","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 1985 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2001"},"text":"section 2001 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
